Note: Core Verification Framework - Advanced formal verification and proof system for AI security
Note: Implements zero-knowledge proofs, formal verification, and cryptographic verification protocols
Note: Designed to exceed academic and enterprise verification systems with AI-first approach

Import "datetime" as DateTime
Import "collections" as Collections

Note: =============================================================================
Note: VERIFICATION TYPES AND CLASSIFICATIONS
Note: =============================================================================

Type called "VerificationType":
    FORMAL_VERIFICATION
    CRYPTOGRAPHIC_PROOF
    ZERO_KNOWLEDGE_PROOF
    BEHAVIORAL_VERIFICATION
    CONSTITUTIONAL_COMPLIANCE
    SECURITY_PROPERTY_VERIFICATION
    AI_SAFETY_VERIFICATION
    PERFORMANCE_VERIFICATION
    INTEGRITY_VERIFICATION
    AUTHENTICITY_VERIFICATION

Type called "VerificationStatus":
    PENDING
    IN_PROGRESS
    VERIFIED
    FAILED
    PARTIALLY_VERIFIED
    REQUIRES_HUMAN_REVIEW
    EXPIRED
    REVOKED

Type called "ProofType":
    INTERACTIVE_PROOF
    NON_INTERACTIVE_PROOF
