    SAFETY
    LIVENESS
    SECURITY
    CORRECTNESS
    PERFORMANCE
    FAIRNESS
    PRIVACY
    CONSTITUTIONAL_COMPLIANCE
    INVARIANT
    PRECONDITION
    POSTCONDITION

Type called "VerificationResult":
